## What This Adds

✅ **Dual-pane UI** - Main text on left, commentary on right
✅ **4 tabs** - Search, Library Browser, Bookmarks, History
✅ **Library tree** - Browse books by category
✅ **Bookmarks** - Star favorite texts (saved to localStorage)
✅ **History** - Auto-tracks last 50 texts read
✅ **Settings panel** - Theme (light/dark/sepia), font size, Hebrew fonts
✅ **Resizable panes** - Drag the divider to adjust widths
✅ **Nikud toggle** - Show/hide vowel points
✅ **Keyboard shortcuts** - Enter to search
✅ **Responsive toolbar** - Close, bookmark, settings buttons

Everything is **persistent** (bookmarks, history, settings survive app restart) and works **immediately** when you run:

```bash
npm run dev
```

This is now a **fully functional** text study app!
