1. **Hebrew search normalization** (search with/without nikud)
2. **Real commentary system** (Rashi, Ramban, etc.)
3. **Verse-by-verse display** with clickable references
4. **Keyboard shortcuts** (power user features)
5. **Export/Copy functionality**
6. **Text cross-references** (click a verse to jump to it)

