## 🌟 What is Otzaria?

Otzaria (אוצריא - "Treasury" in Hebrew) is a complete digital Torah library that brings thousands of years of Jewish texts to your fingertips. Built with modern technology (Rust + Tauri), it's lightning-fast, works offline, and packed with features that make studying Torah a joy.

### Why Otzaria?

- ⚡ **Lightning Fast** - Search thousands of texts in milliseconds
- 🎨 **Beautiful Design** - Modern, clean interface that doesn't get in the way
- 🔒 **100% Private** - Everything runs locally, no data sent anywhere
- 🆓 **Free Forever** - Open source, no subscriptions, no ads
- 🌙 **Made for Study** - Features designed by students, for students

---

## ✨ Features

### 🔍 Advanced Search
- Search in Hebrew **with or without vowel points** (nikud)
- Boolean operators: `light AND darkness`, `Moses OR Aaron`
- Exact phrases: `"in the beginning"`
- Wildcards: `אור*` finds all words starting with אור
- Search history for quick access to past searches

### 📖 Study Interface
- **Multi-pane layouts** - View up to 4 texts simultaneously
- **Dual-pane mode** - Text and commentary side-by-side
- **Smart text display** - Verses numbered, references clickable
- **Focus mode** - Distraction-free reading (Ctrl+Shift+F)
- **Night mode** - Easy on the eyes for late-night study

### 📝 Personal Study Tools
- **Notes** - Add notes to any verse with tags
- **Highlights** - 5 colors for marking important passages
- **Bookmarks** - Save your favorite texts
- **Collections** - Organize texts by topic or theme
- **Workspaces** - Save and restore your study layout

### 🗂️ Flashcards & Memory
- Create flashcards from any text
- **Spaced repetition** algorithm (SM-2)
- Track review schedule automatically
- Perfect for memorization

### ⏱️ Study Tracking
- **Study sessions** - Track time spent studying
- **Statistics** - See total hours, texts studied, notes taken
- **Reading progress** - Resume where you left off
- **Daily study** - See today's Parsha and Daf Yomi

### 🔢 Hebrew Tools
- **Gematria calculator** - Calculate numerical values
- Shows transliteration and word roots
- Right-click any Hebrew word for instant calculation

### 📚 Library Management
- Import texts from Sefaria API
- Support for TXT, JSON formats
- Auto-indexing on startup
- Browse by category (Torah, Talmud, Commentary, etc.)

### 🎯 Power Features
- **Text comparison** - Compare multiple texts side-by-side
- **Text statistics** - Word frequency, verse count, analysis
- **Citation generator** - Traditional, Academic, BibTeX formats
- **Export** - Plain text, Markdown, HTML
- **Text-to-speech** - Listen to Hebrew texts
