## 🐛 Troubleshooting

### App Won't Start

```bash
# Clean reinstall
rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json
nix develop
npm install
npm run dev
```

### No Search Results

**Solution 1:** Reindex the library
- Open Settings (Ctrl + ,)
- Click **🔄 Reindex Library**
- Wait 10-30 seconds

**Solution 2:** Check library folder
```bash
ls library/
# Should show: Torah, Talmud, Commentary, etc.
```

### Texts Not Showing

Make sure you have texts downloaded:
```bash
python3 scripts/download_library.py
```

Or create a test file:
```bash
mkdir -p library/Torah
echo "Test text בראשית" > library/Torah/test.txt
```

Restart the app - it will auto-index.

### Search Too Slow

If you have 10,000+ texts:
- Close unused panes
- Clear search history (🕐 History → Clear)
- Reduce results limit in search filters

### Build Errors

```bash
# Clean Rust build
cd src-tauri
cargo clean
cd ..

# Rebuild
nix develop
npm run build
```

