### Can I use it on Windows/Mac?

Currently optimized for Linux/NixOS. Windows/Mac support possible - contributions welcome!

### How do I back up my data?

Click 💾 **Backup** button → **📤 Export Data**. Save the JSON file somewhere safe.

### Can I import from other apps?

Currently supports TXT and JSON. Convert your texts to these formats and put in `library/`.

### How big can my library be?

Tested with 10,000+ texts. The search index handles millions of documents efficiently.

### Is my data private?

100% private. Nothing is sent anywhere. All data stays on your computer.

### Can I customize the search?

Yes! Use boolean operators, wildcards, and filters. See [Advanced Search](#-advanced-search) above.

