## Troubleshooting

### App won't start
```bash
rm -rf node_modules
nix develop
npm install
npm run dev
```

### No search results
1. Open Settings (`Ctrl+,`)
2. Click "Reindex Library"
3. Wait 10-30 seconds

### No texts showing
Download texts:
```bash
python3 scripts/download_library.py
```

Or create a test file:
```bash
mkdir -p library/Torah
echo "בראשית" > library/Torah/test.txt
```

### Build errors
```bash
cd src-tauri
cargo clean
cd ..
npm run build
```

